description: Advenica AB engages in the provision of cybersecurity solutions focusing on intrusions, theft, and data leakage. The company is headquartered in Malmo, Skane and currently employs 49 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2014-09-18. The company is engaged in communications security by providing products and solutions aimed at secure network communication and secure information exchange. Its product portfolio includes virtual private network (VPN) encryptors, data diodes, self-erasing universal serial bus (USB) devices, solutions for secure video conferencing, cross domain security solutions, and accessories, such as power supplies, interface converters, and mounts, among others. Additionally, the Company offers services, such as network design, security evaluation and penetration testing, implementation and adaptation, and after sales services. Its customers include military, government agencies, police authorities, financial institutions and corporations.
name: Advenica AB (publ)
